{
  "abstract": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "Direct the movements and animation of models."
    }
  ],
  "primaryContentSections": [
    {
      "kind": "content",
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "Overview",
          "level": 2,
          "type": "heading",
          "text": "Overview"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Games and immersive game-like experiences often rely on animated character models to represent the player or non-player characters."
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "The "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "CharacterControllerComponent"
            },
            {
              "text": " simplifies the process of moving a character around a scene.",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "It handles basic movement, including navigating up and down stairs and slopes and jumping."
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " "
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "It also allows you to sync the character movement with specific animations."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "To further animate models in the scene, you may need to define a ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.RealityKit/documentation/RealityKit/SkeletalPose",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " or adopt a full",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "inverse kinematics solution with "
            },
            {
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference",
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.RealityKit/documentation/RealityKit/IKComponent"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
